      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello, my name is Xiao Ping (XP). I&amp;rsquo;m currently at the Singapore-ETH Centre working under a research project on &amp;lsquo;ecosystem services&amp;rsquo;, which aims to understand how we can improve the ecological performance of urban greenery through landscape design. Outside of research, I enjoy playing the drums and going for adventure sports. Feel free to contact me via &lt;a href=&#34;#contact&#34;&gt;email&lt;/a&gt; or on social media if you&amp;rsquo;re interested to connect!&lt;/p&gt;
